graph TB
    subgraph "KubeRay Operator Namespace (opendatahub)"
        Operator[KubeRay Operator<br/>Go Operator<br/>Port: 8080, 8081]
        Webhook[Validating Webhook<br/>Port: 9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ mTLS]
        Operator -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "User Namespace"
        subgraph "Ray Cluster (RayCluster CR)"
            HeadPod[Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS Server<br/>Dashboard<br/>Scheduler]
            Worker1[Ray Worker Pod 1]
            Worker2[Ray Worker Pod 2]
            WorkerN[Ray Worker Pod N]
            Autoscaler[Ray Autoscaler<br/>Sidecar Container]

            HeadPod -->|coordinates| Worker1
            HeadPod -->|coordinates| Worker2
            HeadPod -->|coordinates| WorkerN
            Autoscaler -.->|monitors| HeadPod
        end

        subgraph "Services"
            HeadSvc[Head Service<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard<br/>10001/TCP Client]
            ServeSvc[Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP]
            MetricsSvc[Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        end

        HeadSvc -->|routes to| HeadPod
        ServeSvc -->|routes to| HeadPod
        MetricsSvc -->|routes to| HeadPod
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayJobCR[RayJob CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayServiceCR[RayService CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates via kubectl| RayClusterCR
    User -->|submits| RayJobCR
    User -->|deploys| RayServiceCR

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| Operator
    RayJobCR -->|watched by| Operator
    RayServiceCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates| HeadPod
    Operator -->|creates| Worker1
    Operator -->|creates| Worker2
    Operator -->|creates| WorkerN
    Operator -->|creates| HeadSvc
    Operator -->|creates| ServeSvc
    Operator -->|creates| MetricsSvc

    Autoscaler -->|scales via K8s API| Operator

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Certificate Mgmt]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
        Redis[External Redis<br/>6379/TCP TCP<br/>GCS Fault Tolerance]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Object Storage]
    end

    Operator -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    Webhook -->|uses certs from| CertManager
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| Operator
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| MetricsSvc
    HeadPod -.->|optional| Redis
    HeadPod -->|checkpoints to| S3
    Worker1 -->|reads from| S3

    subgraph "Ingress/Routes"
        Ingress[Kubernetes Ingress<br/>or OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    ExternalClient[External Client] -->|HTTPS| Ingress
    Ingress -->|8265/TCP| HeadSvc
    Ingress -->|8000/TCP| ServeSvc

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HeadPod fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Worker1 fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Worker2 fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WorkerN fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayJobCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Redis fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
